OL,5, A London law firm has offered staff the
OL,6, option to work from home permanently,  
OL,7, but the convenience comes at a price.  
OL,9,FThe firm, Stephenson Harwood, said it  
OL,10,Fwould allow staff to work remotely but 
OL,11,Fpay them 20% less than their current   
OL,12,Fsalary.                                
OL,14,FSince the start of the pandemic a      
OL,15,Fdebate has raged over who gains and who
OL,16,Floses when staff work from home.       
OL,18,FEmployees save time and money, but     
OL,19,Femployers can save too, on office space
OL,20,Fand costs.                             
